        <abstract> 
<p>The Natural Philosophical Society [Academy of Sciences] will publish his translation of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> in August, before <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>A distinguished member of the Hungarian Parliament attacked CD’s theory. LD answered, and a controversy ensued.</p>
            <p>LD has noted many signs of public support for CD.</p>
        </abstract>
